# Complete AWS Lab Guide

## EC2 (Apache + PHP) ↔ RDS MySQL Inside Same VPC

### Without Creating Separate Security Group for RDS

This guide includes all missing steps and follows a simpler method:

* One VPC
* Public EC2
* RDS in same VPC
* SAME security group used for both EC2 and RDS
* Apache + PHP + MySQL connection test

---

# Architecture

```text
Internet
   |
   v
EC2 (Ubuntu + Apache + PHP)
   |
   v
RDS MySQL
```

Both resources are inside same VPC.

