# STEP 11 — Connect to EC2

Move key to Linux terminal location.

Run:

```bash
chmod 400 mykey.pem
```

Connect:

```bash
ssh -i mykey.pem ubuntu@EC2_PUBLIC_IP
```

Example:

```bash
ssh -i mykey.pem ubuntu@13.234.xx.xx
```

Type:

```bash
