# STEP 12 — Install Apache

Inside EC2:

Update packages:

```bash
sudo apt update -y
```

Install Apache:

```bash
sudo apt install apache2 -y
```

Start Apache:

```bash
sudo systemctl start apache2
sudo systemctl enable apache2
```

Check status:

```bash
sudo systemctl status apache2
```

You should see:

```text
active (running)
```

Press:

```text
Q
```

to exit.

